quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,"Ndiponso kuti chilango changa, ndithudi, ndi chilango chowawa koposa"
  15,51,Auze za alendo a Abrahamu
  15,52,"Pamene iwo adadza kwa iye ndi kumuuza kuti, “Mtendere ukhale kwa iwe.’ Koma iye adawayankha kuti, “Ndili ndi mantha ndi inu.”"
  15,53,"Iwo adati, “Usaope! Ife tadza kwa iwe ndi nkhani yabwino ya mwana wamwamuna amene adzakhala wodziwa zambiri.”"
  15,54,"Iye adati, “Kodi inu muli kudzandiuza nkhani yabwino pamene ine nditakalamba kale? “Kodi nkhani yanu ndi yotani?”"
  15,55,"Iwo adati, “Ife tili kukuuza nkhani yabwinoyi mwachoonadi. Kotero usakhale wotaya mtima.”"
  15,56,"Iye adati, “Ndani amene angataye mtima ndi chifundo cha Mulungu, kupatula osochera?”"
  15,57,"Iye adatinso, “Kodi cholinga chanu ndi chiyani, inu otumidwa?”"
  15,58,"Iwo adati, “Ife tatumidwa kwa anthu oipa.”"
  15,59,"“onse kupatula anthu otsatira Loti okha. Ife, ndithudi, tidzawapulumutsa iwo okha.”"
  15,60,“Kupatula mkazi wake amene ife talamulidwa kuti akhalire m’mbuyo pamodzi ndi iwo amene anali kukhalira m’mbuyo.”
  15,61,Ndipo pamene a Kazembe athu adadza ku nyumba ya Loti
  15,62,"Loti adati, “Ndithudi inu ndinu anthu omwe sindikudziwani.”"
  15,63,"Iwo adati, “Iyayi. Ife takubweretsera iweyo zinthu zimene iwo anali kukayika.”"
  15,64,"“Ndipo Ife tadza ndi choonadi kwa iwe ndipo, ndithudi, ife ndife onena zoona.”"
  15,65,"“Motero choka ndi abale ako pakati pa usiku, iwe uziyenda pambuyo pawo ndipo usalole wina aliyense kuti atembenuke. Kapita kumene walamulidwa kupita.”"
  15,66,Ndipo tidamuuza lamulo ili kuti mizu ya iwo idzazulidwa m’mawa
  15,67,Ndipo anthu a mu Mzinda adadza ali osangala
  15,68,"Iye adati, “Ndithudi! Awa ndi alendo anga motero musandichititse manyazi ayi.”"
  15,69,“opani Mulungu ndipo musandipangitse manyazi.”
  15,70,"Iwo adati, “Kodi ife sitidakuletse kuti uzichereza alendo?”"
  15,71,"Iye adati, “Awa ndi ana anga a aakazi; akwatireni ngati inu mufunadi kutero.”"
  15,72,Ndithudi pali moyo wako! Iwo chifukwa chakuledzera anali kuyenda mwakhungu
  15,73,Ndipo chilango chidawapeza pamene dzuwa linkatuluka
  15,74,Ndipo Ife tidaononga (mizinda yawo) zapansi kukhala pamwamba ndipo tidawagwetsera mvula ya miyala ya moto
  15,75,Ndithudi! Mu izi muli zizindikiro kwa anthu omvetsa
  15,76,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iyo ili m’mphepete mwa msewu umene umapitidwa"
  15,77,Ndithudi! Muizimulizizindikirokwaanthuokhulupirira
  15,78,Ngakhale anthu okhala m’nkhalango nawonso anali ochimwa
  15,79,Motero Ife tidawalanga. Ndipo iwo ali pamalo poonekera
  15,80,"Ndipo, ndithudi, anthu a ku Hijr adakana Atumwi"
  15,81,Ndipo Ife tidawapatsa zizindikiro zathu koma iwo adazikana
  15,82,Ndipo iwo anali kukumba mapiri kukhala nyumba zawo ndipo anali kukhala mosaopa
  15,83,Phokoso la chilango lidafika kwa iwo m’mawa
  15,84,Ndipo sizidawathandize zonse zimene anali kuchita
  15,85,"Ndipo Ife sitidalenge kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pawo kupatula ndi choonadi. Ndithudi popanda chikayiko tsiku lachiweruzo lidzadza; kotero akhululukireni, kukhululuka kwabwino"
  15,86,Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndi Namalenga ndi wodziwa zinthu zonse
  15,87,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidakupatsa mavesi asanu ndi awiri amene amanenedwa kawirikawiri ndi Korani yolemekezeka"
  15,88,Usamayang’ane mwanjiru zinthu zokoma zimene tawapatsa ena a iwo kapena kumamva chisoni pa izo. Ndipo onetsani chifundo kwa anthu okhulupirira
  15,89,"Ndipo Nena, “Ine ndine Mchenjezi”"
  15,90,Monga tidatumiza kwa amene amagawanitsa
  15,91,Amene apanga Buku la Korani kukhala magawo awiri
  15,92,"Kotero, pali Ambuye wako, tidzawafunsa"
  15,93,Pa zonse zimene anali kuchita
  15,94,"Motero lalikira poyera zonse zimene walamulidwa, ndipo choka pakati pa osakhulupirira"
  15,95,Ndithudi Ife tidzakuteteza kwa onyoza
  15,96,Iwo amene amatumikira mulungu wina kuonjezera pa Mulungu weniweni iwowo adzadziwa
  15,97,Ndithudi Ife tilikudziwakutizimakupweteka mumtima mwako zinthu zimene amanena
  15,98,Motero lemekeza Ambuye wako ndipo khala mmodzi wa iwo amene amagwada pomulemekeza Iye
  15,99,Ndipo pembedza Ambuye wako mpaka pamene ola lotsimikizidwa likupeza